rooms.Name: Inside a prison cell
rooms.Description:
You are standing inside a prison cell.  The door is in front of you,
while you can see a hallway running left and right.

rooms.Name: Outside a cell, standing in the middle of a hallway
rooms.Description:
You are standing outside a cell, there are nazi's coming from everywhere.
The sirens are blaring and you know you are in trouble.

hear men's voices around you speaking German.  The hallway runs east
and west.

and west.  As you stand admiring the grey walls, the voices of German 
soldiers rings in your ears.  You feel the need to keep on moving.

You are standing at a split in the path, go east, or go west, you can hear
the sound of a helicopter a helicopter in the background, the sound
is loudest coming from the east.

rooms.Name: A Hallway
rooms.Description:
The sounds of the helicopter are deafening, you can see the chopper and
you might be able to catch the REAL Adolph if you run!

rooms.Name: A Hallway
rooms.Description:
The sound of the chopper is about even now, coming from either direction,
but you can feel the beat of the air coming from the north.

rooms.Name: A Hallway
rooms.Description:
You can hear the chopper very loudly now, though it is taking a little
longer then you thought to get to the chopper, better start running now.

rooms.Name: Entrance to the 2nd Level
rooms.Description:
You are standing before a large steel door.  There is a large "2" imprinted
on the door itself.

rooms.Name: a secret
rooms.Description:
You have found a secret!, Congrats ya ding-a-ling, cause the SS knew
about the secret LONG before you did!.
Have fun and die well.

rooms.Name: Entrance to the 2nd Level
rooms.Description:
You are on the other sie of the large steel door.  It looks identical
to the first floor, except it is reversed of the last.

rooms.Name: a secret
rooms.Description:
Congrats, you have found a secret!  Unfortunately, The SS Commander knows
about this secret as well.

rooms.Name: Entrance to the 3rd Level
rooms.Description:
You are standing before the Entrance to the 3rd level.  There is a large
steel door before you, it is bolted closed and there is only a small
key hole.  You try and pick at it, but it shocks you, this is key only.

rooms.Name: Entrance to the 3rd Level
rooms.Description:
You are standing within the 3rd level entrance, unlike the other 2 levels,
the hall runs north from the entrance, you can hear men banging on the
door behind you, better run now before you get it!

rooms.Name: A secret conference room
rooms.Description:
You have found the secret conference room.  Before you stands a man that
looks just like Adolph Hitler, but, for some reason, just isn't.

rooms.Name: Loh and behold, a secret!
rooms.Description:
You thought this zone was done and over with didn't you!  Aha, only
you have realized that Adolph was a CLONE!, find the real adolph and
find the real key.

rooms.Name: A teleporter back to the end, congrats!
rooms.Description:
Congrats, you have finished what you thought was the end of the game,
but the message appears on your screen..........




Loh and behold the REAL Adolph has fled the scene, thanks for letting
him get away, the whole world is going to die, it is all your fault!

rooms.Name: On the helipad
rooms.Description:
You jump out onto the tarmack and....



You were ONE SECOND TOO late, the chopper has just lifted off and flies
away while you can stand there doing nothing.  As you turn
around you realize that a steel door has closed and slammed behind you.
There is nothing left to do but jump off the roof and pray that
There is a way home.

ExtraDescs.Description:
You see a steel door that is closed, there is NO WAY for you to go
south, just jump, Sheol has made it easy for you.

rooms.Name: On the helipad
rooms.Description:
You got here JUST IN TIME, a steel door closes behind you.

Adolph Hitler looks at you.

Adolph Hitler says 'It is you unt me now!'

rooms.Name: Within the helicopter
rooms.Description:
Congratulations!  You have destroyed the nazi regime and killed the leaders!
You take a Loooooooong look at the helicopter pilot, he looks back at you
smiles, shows you a card.

Roger, CIA

Enjoy the ride home, mission: ACCOMPLISHED.

rooms.Name: Entrance to the Cyborg lab
rooms.Description:
You have found the secret zone in Wolfenstein.  There are red flashing
lights around you.  There are no alarms as you enter here.  This is not
usual for the zone as you have seen.  I would be weary here, this is going
to be very hard in comparison to the topside.

rooms.Description:
You are standing within the cyborg lab, there are incomplete cyborgs standing
and watching you with red eyes.  You should just destroy them while you are
here.

There are 2 large cyborgs, not as big as the one you encountered at
the beginning of the area, but these 2 guys are real big.  You small
a small man huddling in the back.

rooms.Name: A secret mission: NEWBIES BEWARE! HIGH LEVEL ONLY
rooms.Description:
Welcome soldier boy/girl/thing!.  You think you are tuff enough to  take
out a world threat, then you just go NORTH.  But, if you are under level 45
please, do not enter this area, you will DIE!
